parameters: Mamiko: "I won't tell anyone, so please help me--"

Mamiko: "Eh, who are you? There was supposed to be a man in black in
this room..."

Yui: "If you're talking about the man in black, he just left this
room."

Mamiko: "I... I found out the secret of the shop! And then I was
chased by that guy in black! And, and! That's why I'm here!"

Yui: "Calm down, please! I'll listen to what happened, so take your
time..."

Yui: "Was it the man who was shouting in this room earlier that caused
this?"

Mamiko: "Yes... I was working as a hostess at a shop next to this
building called \C[17]Agas\C[0]..."

Mamiko: "Something happened that led me to discover the terrifying
secret of the shop, and I got scared and tried to quit..."
Mamiko: "Then that guy questioned me about my reasons..."

Mamiko: "When I told him that I had discovered the shop's secret, he
suddenly changed his attitude and locked me up in the basement."

Mamiko: "But I managed to escape when I saw an opportunity, only to be
found by him and chased."
Yui: "What's the secret of the shop?"

Mamiko: "That place, they were forcibly keeping girls locked up in the
basement."

Mamiko: "Down there, they were forced to shoot adult videos, and the
girls were being used as tools for making money."

Mamiko: "I accidentally recorded the manager locking up one of the
girls with my smartphone..."

Yui: "Then let's go to the police together. We'll hand over that
evidence! If we have proof, the police will surely act."
Mamiko: "The thing is, he took my smartphone."
Mamiko: "By now, it's probably already back with the manager..."

Yui: "Understood. I'll get it back! And we have to free the girls who
are locked up in the basement too!"
Mamiko: "How can you possibly do that..."
Yui: "Don't worry, I'm confident about these things."

Mamiko: "First off, without this permit, you won't be recognized as
staff and won't even be able to enter."

Mamiko: "It's a cosplay costume exclusive to Agas. If you're a female
staff member, you need to wear it or you'll be considered an
outsider."

Mamiko: "I've never met someone as brave as you before. Please, save
everyone."
Yui: "Of course. Leave it to me!"

Mamiko: "\C[17]Agas\C[0] is in the shop next to this building. Please,
save everyone."
Mamiko: "Eh...? The passcode for the confinement room?"
Mamiko: "I'm sorry. I don't know that..."

Mamiko: "But, knowing the manager, it might be related to some number
that's significant to him. If there's anything in \c[17]the manager's
room\c[0] that could be a hint..."
